'''卡蘭吉田火山'''是[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]][[北蘇拉威西省|北蘇拉威西省]]的[[火山|火山]]，位於[[錫奧島|錫奧島]]北部，自1675年有41次[[火山爆發|火山爆發]]，是印度尼西亞最活躍的火山之一。1997年3人因火山爆發造成的[[火山碎屑流|火山碎屑流]]死亡。2010年8月6日，卡蘭吉田火山爆發，[[熔岩|熔岩]]和火山灰噴至數百米高空，4人失蹤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/A/AS_INDONESIA_VOLCANIC_ERUPTION?SITE=KTVB&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT |title=Volcano in eastern Indonesia erupts; several people seriously hurt |access-date=2010-11-07 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031142133/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/A/AS_INDONESIA_VOLCANIC_ERUPTION?SITE=KTVB&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5iX0zLJU4yX9omqKMiAy2H7-Z7zHAD9HDUN384 |title=Volcano erupts in eastern Indonesia |accessdate=2010-11-07 |archive-date=2010-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901104941/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5iX0zLJU4yX9omqKMiAy2H7-Z7zHAD9HDUN384 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

